Buck Connors https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buck_Connors 0 Buck Connors (November 22, 1880 – February 4, 1947) was an American actor. He appeared in 85 films between 1912 and 1941. The son of William L Conner and Leah Bowen, Buck was born in Streator, La Salle County, Illinois, and died in Quartzsite, Arizona. Buck is buried in Hi Jolly Cemetery in Quartzsite.
